{"tid":2327672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"十二年前(2008)FB已經審查同ban帳戶","createTime":"2020-12-16T08:36:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T08:36:22.000Z","uid":20867,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6e7537aeca0ccf0fafba944f69328c86834724f4","tid":2327672,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T08:36:22.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">【本報訊】奧運聖火來港前夕，除有外國人士遭無理拒絕入境外，連計劃手持雪山獅子旗抗議示威的香港大學女生陳巧文的 facebook賬戶，昨日亦突然遭取消，而賬戶中用以聯絡參加示威活動人士的群組，亦突然「失靈」，多次出現不能開的情況，陳不排除事件涉及政治因素，她憂慮網上的言論自由進一步被收窄。</code></pre><br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/amp/4434454/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Famp%2F4434454%2Fpage%2F1&d=P3odlOe4J5oN5vIqyIzMU02FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=14f3a174\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/amp/4434454/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OIHECYSBFFJ5G5IHXRQSLH4ULY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOIHECYSBFFJ5G5IHXRQSLH4ULY.jpg&h=e8f112cb&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}